aim</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Michael-Kiwanuka">Michael Kiwanuka</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Turnstile">Turnstile</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-reveal-2025-day-splits-for-line-up-3812298">《Primavera Sound》公布 2025 年阵容的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
